      'result': """The "ET EXPLOIT [PTsecurity] DoublePulsar Backdoor installation communication" signature refers to the detection of the DoublePulsar backdoor, a sophisticated kernel-mode implant. While a specific signature history for "ET EXPLOIT [PTsecurity]" under that exact name could not be definitively traced through public records, the DoublePulsar backdoor itself has a well-documented history following its public disclosure.

